(16022, 'Cefobid 1 gm vial (i.v-i.m)', 'سيفوبيد 1جم فيال', '72', '104', 'Cefoperazone', 'Pfizer', 'Vial', 'فيال', '', 'Antibiotic.cephalosporin.third-generation', '1 gm', 'Indicated for the treatment of following infections caused by susceptible bacteria:[label]
